title: Call the Midwife by Jennifer Worth
description:
The memoirs by Jennifer Worth that has been turned into a hit BBC/Masterpiece series Call The Midwife.

In the 1950s, twenty-two-year-old Jenny Lee leaves her comfortable home to move into a convent and become a midwife in London's East End slums.
